{"title":"将军上哨（二首）","authors":["郑南"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":3,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军上哨（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公安部队某部　郑南"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军徽映得晨星退，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草鞋震得朝露碎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军走向哨所来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粗布挎包身上背。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远远望见将军影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十二个战士往门外飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看着将军见亲人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不眨眼啊不动眉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军鬓发白如雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年枕着雪山睡；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腿上伤疤留印迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年在枣林追白匪……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军走过的革命路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比咱全班多几倍？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军不该来哨所，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看你一把老年岁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军笑声响如雷："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们都是战斗队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们年青站排头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我多几岁当排尾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军摘下布挎包，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一张军图摊上腿："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共商讨啊共研究，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这座大山怎保卫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送别将军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军前边走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士身后随，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人都想问一句："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天去了几时回？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话在嘴边转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁也不出嘴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军整月在哨所，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶着风雨守边陲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和咱同锅吃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和咱同炕睡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军装褪了几层色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸膛晒得红又黑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腿是送他走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心在盼他回。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过一山又一山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涉过一水又一水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军的命令不生效，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫谁归去谁不归。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一直送过大山背，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心底话儿才出嘴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士对着山谷喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军同志几时回？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山谷代替将军答："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天去了明天回。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}